Landing Page Structure

এখন পুরো landing page structure দিলাম।

1. Hero Section

সবচেয়ে important section।

Left Side

Big headline:

Example:

Transition Into Retirement With Confidence & Purpose

Subheading:

Discover personalized insights, readiness assessments,
and guidance designed to help you thrive in retirement.

Buttons:

Take Assessment
Learn More
Right Side

Image:

older professional couple
calm lifestyle
beach/walking/laptop/coffee vibe

NOT:

overly old people
hospital vibe
depressing retirement look
2. Trust/Statistics Section

Example:

30+ Years of Behavioral Psychology Experience
Helping Professionals Navigate Retirement Transition

Cards:

Psychology-Based Guidance
Progress Tracking
Personalized Assessments
Expert Insights
3. “Why Retirement Feels Difficult” Section

Emotional connection section।

Topics:

loss of identity
lack of structure
purpose confusion
emotional transition

This section will emotionally hook users.

4. Assessment System Section

MOST IMPORTANT SECTION.

Explain:

how assessment works
personalized insights
progress tracking
readiness scoring

Possible flow UI:

Step 1 → Answer Questions
Step 2 → Get Personalized Insights
Step 3 → Track Your Progress

CTA:

Start Assessment
5. Features Section

Cards/grid:

Retirement Readiness Assessments
Personalized Progress Tracking
Expert Psychological Guidance
Structured Growth Plans
Educational Resources
Community & Support
6. About Dave Section

Very important for trust.

Use:

professional image
short story
psychology background
why he created platform

This makes website human.

7. Book Promotion Section

Since client already selling book.

Section:

book mockup
short description
benefits
Buy Now button
8. Testimonials Section

Later client reviews add করবে।

Now placeholder রাখতে পারো।

9. Blog / Resources Preview

3 latest articles show করবা।

Example:

Finding Purpose After Retirement
Building Structure In Daily Life
The Psychology of Transition
10. Newsletter Section

Lead generation।

Headline:

Get Weekly Retirement Transition Insights

Input:

email
subscribe button
11. Final CTA Section

Strong emotional CTA।

Example:

Retirement Is Not The End Of Your Story
It’s The Beginning Of A New Chapter

Button:

Take Your Assessment
