Important UX Advice

Audience older professionals।

So:

✅ bigger font
✅ high contrast
✅ calm colors
✅ clean spacing
✅ easy navigation
✅ no clutter

Avoid:
❌ flashy animation
❌ tiny fonts
❌ complex layout
❌ too much scrolling confusion

Best Color Direction
Navy Blue
Soft White
Warm Gray
Muted Green
Light Beige
